query:
query questionData($titleSlug: String!) {
  question(titleSlug: $titleSlug) {
    questionId
    questionFrontendId
    title
    titleSlug
    content
    translatedTitle
    translatedContent
    isPaidOnly
    difficulty
    likes
    dislikes
    isLiked
    langToValidPlayground
    stats
    hints
    status
    sampleTestCase
    judgeType
  }
}
